OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy firms face probe    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover prepayment meters     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy firms are to be investigated by 
OL,6, the industry regulator following a     
OL,7, sharp rise in the number of households 
OL,8, being forced onto prepayment meters.   
OL,10,FThe regulator, Ofgem, is also warning  
OL,11,Ffirms it will take legal action if they
OL,12,Fare not taking proper due care of      
OL,13,Fvulnerable households.                 
OL,15,FOn Sunday, the government said         
OL,16,Fsuppliers should stop forcing          
OL,17,Fhouseholds onto prepayment meters.     
OL,19,FOfgem is also considering cheaper      
OL,20,Fsocial tariffs for some on low incomes.
